// The histogram function computes the frequency of each integer in the input sequence.
// The input sequence 'In' contains unsigned integers, and 'buckets' specifies the
// number of bins, corresponding to the range [0, buckets-1].
//
// The implementation uses a hybrid strategy to achieve optimal performance across
