  // This implementation uses a hybrid strategy to be fast for all input sizes.
  // It chooses between two algorithms based on the number of buckets.

  // Threshold for switching strategies. This is a heuristic based on when the
  // total size of per-thread local histograms (num_workers * buckets) is
  // likely to exceed the L3 cache, making random accesses to them slow.
  // 1 << 16 = 65536 buckets. For 100 workers, this is 100 * 65536 * 4B ~= 26MB.
